{"tid":1458714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我好驚今日大家出黎發洩完之後 聽日又開始少人","createTime":"2019-08-12T14:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T15:13:37.000Z","uid":166755,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e27119c38e2bf4b79afb50616ae5205d9302bee8","tid":1458714,"uid":166755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:46:52.000Z","msg":"我相信大家因爲琴日黑警啲事睇完好嬲 今日就咁多人出咗黎 但記住 未來幾日都要繼續 大家都知機場對香港既影響有幾大 大家要加油 一齊撐落去！比返個交代烈士 義士 同 受咗傷既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港人加油！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jyoKCRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjyoKCRG.png&h=ee76ec6d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B8yVKwH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB8yVKwH.png&h=f48696c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xbeqnio.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxbeqnio.png&h=26c259a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"113587347c54f3c2c0470ae0bdb574985156226d","tid":1458714,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:47:10.000Z","msg":"[賽後檢討] 抗爭者進化史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1458526\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1458526</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3e7c6715308a110b8cf21d5bae5156de5834e3d9","tid":1458714,"uid":166755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:47:35.000Z","msg":"香港人加油"},{"pid":"78decdaa948d029af3ae72a0bc3b5af35c1012c1","tid":1458714,"uid":166755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:47:45.000Z","msg":"一齊贏"},{"pid":"830b49173b39736d8428171956313759878ec4be","tid":1458714,"uid":166755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:47:57.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},{"pid":"6c0c8099a09f877e53f797acfba3adcf236e0338","tid":1458714,"uid":22009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:48:24.000Z","msg":"希望大家諗諗快閃模式適唔適合大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1458545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1458545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a65b16a824570e98aec195548cd3b74f514164f6","tid":1458714,"uid":166755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:48:32.000Z","msg":"不分化 不割𥱊！"},{"pid":"7dd2cd90953d131c845d4c357bd52d73a7f7df03","tid":1458714,"uid":166755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:49:00.000Z","msg":"未來呢幾日都要頂住！！"},{"pid":"e9249f2b6e45cacdd81ff1acd6874f9aad1ccf0a","tid":1458714,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:49:29.000Z","msg":"pppppush pppppush pppppush"},{"pid":"ceb83f4ac748b586efe95af64035dc7b35dd021e","tid":1458714,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:50:06.000Z","msg":"大家知道有效就上晒電<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bdae808f6312367b9c54fbbb3f6a885236ca7f7","tid":1458714,"uid":166755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:50:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RVwwhS4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRVwwhS4.png&h=488a10e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"454bf7ab6e55d175d03403ab5e91500b415bccbb","tid":1458714,"uid":166755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:50:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"e426293fd15a060562f57b9f27dd7868a9806cee","tid":1458714,"uid":299253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:51:40.000Z","msg":"點會咁就完 聽日會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />更加多人黎"},{"pid":"68812a36566311d7f79a1ff7684c4feb3d92585b","tid":1458714,"uid":166755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:51:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40b303eaf03b5a56c81633f886e5da1028f9f6e5","tid":1458714,"uid":254361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:51:50.000Z","msg":"借位講幾句野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我求下各位巴打絲打<br />\n用下個腦諗嘢，要自主思考呀<br />\n留又好，唔留又好請交給在場人士去決定<br />\n你哋唔好喺度發文喺度煽動<br />\n佢地成功分化我地了啦<br />\n<br />\n和理非非會驚好多野係正常<br />\n（唔驚又有行動力做左勇武）<br />\n但係但係呢到我有幾句野想講<br />\n<br />\n直面面對「恐怖」，知道它的「傷害」<br />\n理解會造成的「後果」，站起來、面對它<br />\n這才是「勇氣」，這才是「抗爭」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有沒有看過周星馳的電影「少林足球」<br />\n當然還有其他優秀的電影，如「讓子彈飛一會」「V怪客」等等<br />\n<br />\n「少林足球」里的大反派說了這麼幾句<br />\n<br />\n強雄：「我是打人,怎麼樣? 我要把你全隊的人打得像你一樣殘廢、殘廢、殘廢... 跟我鬥?」<br />\n強雄：「還有球證、旁證加上主辦、協辦所有的單位，全部都是我的人，怎麼和我鬥?」<br />\n<br />\n係呀點鬥呀，只剩下咩可以去鬥呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以用你的力量與聲音，用你的方法去「抗爭」<br />\n力量聲音沒分大細，沒分方法嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加油呀，香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後再講返幾句名言<br />\n曼德拉語錄:<br />\n如果天空是黑暗的，那就摸黑生存;<br />\n如果發出聲音是危險的，那就保持沉默;<br />\n如果自覺無力發光，那就蜷伏於牆角。<br />\n但是，不要習慣了黑暗就為黑暗辯護;<br />\n也不要為自己的苟且而得意;<br />\n不要嘲諷那些比自己更勇敢的人。<br />\n我們可以卑微如塵土，但不可扭曲如蛆蟲。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;曼德拉《漫漫人生路》"},{"pid":"307c4dcd81efc75d956483bdb845df63bcfc751d","tid":1458714,"uid":166755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:52:14.000Z","msg":"一日比一日多！！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2409587baa016b7200434e92f5a87206fbaed2b3","tid":1458714,"uid":65264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:52:16.000Z","msg":"比啲信心 同時呼籲下"},{"pid":"dab873af730ec34f3aaf27c552a6d9e4caf68406","tid":1458714,"uid":166755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:53:16.000Z","msg":"我呼籲大家呢幾日都要出黎"},{"pid":"bb8e505d1140f273d7e8fde101813cfd3e077ae3","tid":1458714,"uid":229553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:58:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8.13 1pm 再入機場</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n入嚟投票啊<br />\n8月大型和平遊行 - 遊行/死線/升級日期<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/DypuBRZ6q39uCKeY6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FDypuBRZ6q39uCKeY6&d=1ZU4T503J%2FBBtE%2F0CauWlTe9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=907248c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/DypuBRZ6q39uCKeY6</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w392mWr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw392mWr.jpg&h=4576e766&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oHuJQP4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoHuJQP4.jpg&h=c5748bc9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jNxu1GJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjNxu1GJ.jpg&h=64932c27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WVOuhe4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWVOuhe4.jpg&h=a6d636f1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K4DKCUD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK4DKCUD.jpg&h=ba6c99d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b9b191952296f1a73754cf5e26085e1335db5dc","tid":1458714,"uid":182575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:59:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46c65037493f40aebf32fa0306a5a80ec0f5d1ba","tid":1458714,"uid":204625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:04:05.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"76d9c7f6df5460b411fba08c0c72dba399fac891","tid":1458714